            <title><![CDATA[[话筒]#胁迫诱骗未成年人裸聊明确为猥亵# - 转发 @央视新闻:&ensp;#胁迫诱骗未成年人裸聊明确为猥亵#【“两高”发布司法解释：#从严惩处强奸猥亵等性侵害未成年...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%83%81%E8%BF%AB%E8%AF%B1%E9%AA%97%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E8%A3%B8%E8%81%8A%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E4%B8%BA%E7%8C%A5%E4%BA%B5%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%83%81%E8%BF%AB%E8%AF%B1%E9%AA%97%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E8%A3%B8%E8%81%8A%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E4%B8%BA%E7%8C%A5%E4%BA%B5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#胁迫诱骗未成年人裸聊明确为猥亵#</span></a><br><blockquote> - 转发 <a href="https://weibo.com/2656274875" target="_blank">@央视新闻</a>: <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%83%81%E8%BF%AB%E8%AF%B1%E9%AA%97%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E8%A3%B8%E8%81%8A%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E4%B8%BA%E7%8C%A5%E4%BA%B5%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%83%81%E8%BF%AB%E8%AF%B1%E9%AA%97%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E8%A3%B8%E8%81%8A%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E4%B8%BA%E7%8C%A5%E4%BA%B5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#胁迫诱骗未成年人裸聊明确为猥亵#</span></a>【“两高”发布司法解释：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BB%8E%E4%B8%A5%E6%83%A9%E5%A4%84%E5%BC%BA%E5%A5%B8%E7%8C%A5%E4%BA%B5%E7%AD%89%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E5%AE%B3%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E7%8A%AF%E7%BD%AA%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BB%8E%E4%B8%A5%E6%83%A9%E5%A4%84%E5%BC%BA%E5%A5%B8%E7%8C%A5%E4%BA%B5%E7%AD%89%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E5%AE%B3%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E7%8A%AF%E7%BD%AA%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#从严惩处强奸猥亵等性侵害未成年人犯罪#</span></a>】今天，最高法、最高检发文明确：①对未成年女性负有特殊职责的人员，利用优势地位或者被害人孤立无援的境地，迫使被害人与其发生性关系的，以法定刑较重的强奸罪定罪处罚；②奸淫幼女致其轻伤或者感染严重性病的，应予以加重处罚，不要求达到重伤；③对胁迫、诱骗未成年人进行网络裸聊、向未成年人索要裸照、视频等特殊猥亵行为，明确以猥亵儿童罪或者强制猥亵罪定罪处罚。详↓<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%AF%B9%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E5%AE%B3%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E7%8A%AF%E7%BD%AA%E4%BB%8E%E4%B8%A5%E6%83%A9%E5%A4%84%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%AF%B9%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E5%AE%B3%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E7%8A%AF%E7%BD%AA%E4%BB%8E%E4%B8%A5%E6%83%A9%E5%A4%84%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#对性侵害未成年人犯罪从严惩处#</span></a>（总台央视记者李可婧 李明） <a href="https://weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309404905228528124267" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_article_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">“两高”发布司法解释：从严惩处强奸、猥亵等性侵害未成年人犯罪</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/002TLsr9ly1heaeq50vixj60rs0fmmz002.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br></blockquote>]]></description>
